import React from 'react'
import { Divider, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const DividerExampleInverted = () => (
    <Segment inverted>
        <Divider inverted />
        <Divider horizontal inverted>
        Horizontal
        </Divider>
    </Segment>
)

export default DividerExampleInverted
